{"tid":839612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷竊及欺詐校方逾62萬元 廠商會中學前行政主任被控17罪","createTime":"2018-09-28T05:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T07:17:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7513f7a1d916b6eae1657f25bde0a633eaa7b2dd","tid":839612,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vo5K8yzi9fSH6Oo3tAPRJQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180928a103841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fvo5K8yzi9fSH6Oo3tAPRJQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180928a103841.jpg&h=0709715a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】廠商會中學行政主任及校務處主管，涉嫌利用欺詐手段誘使學校訂購逾30萬元的食物、窗簾及桌椅，使用虛假發票申領9700元以供應盆栽，及盜竊該中學逾31.8萬元款項，被廉署拘控、今於西九龍裁判法院提堂，毋須答辯，需等候文件轉介至區域法院，案件押後到下月18日再訊，被告獲保釋候審。<br />\n<br />\n53歲被告劉賽華案發時擔任職廠商會中學行政主任及校務處主管，負責監督及管理學校的會計及行政事宜。廉署早前接獲投訴，調查後落案控告劉3項欺詐罪、一項使用虛假文書及13項盜竊，共17項控罪。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：陳楚琨"},{"pid":"5a28a19af10ffb6ced1db30f5caa4e900e602dd3","tid":839612,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"呢間印像中...出名打架"},{"pid":"66eac85f061083b6d2f6ee78f0bbff6da9ad7ca8","tid":839612,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}